[
  {
    "text": "This is a council meeting session.",
    "start": 272.32,
    "duration": 6.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Please rise for the pledge of allegiance",
    "start": 274.08,
    "duration": 4.92
  },
  {
    "text": "to the flag of the United States of",
    "start": 280.16,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "America and to the republic for which it",
    "start": 282.24,
    "duration": 5.6
  },
  {
    "text": "stands. One nation under God,",
    "start": 284.88,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "indivisible, with liberty and justice",
    "start": 287.84,
    "duration": 3.359
  },
  {
    "text": "for all.",
    "start": 290.16,
    "duration": 2.64
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Please remain standing for the",
    "start": 291.199,
    "duration": 4.601
  },
  {
    "text": "invocation.",
    "start": 292.8,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Thank you.",
    "start": 297.36,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Esteemed members of the Syracuse Common",
    "start": 299.759,
    "duration": 3.521
  },
  {
    "text": "Council, guests and friends, I am",
    "start": 301.84,
    "duration": 3.76
  },
  {
    "text": "honored to offer today's invocation. Let",
    "start": 303.28,
    "duration": 4.479
  },
  {
    "text": "us pray.",
    "start": 305.6,
    "duration": 3.92
  },
  {
    "text": "God of many faiths and many faith",
    "start": 307.759,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "traditions,",
    "start": 309.52,
    "duration": 5.519
  },
  {
    "text": "all wise, full of grace, full of mercy,",
    "start": 311.039,
    "duration": 6.321
  },
  {
    "text": "and full of love. As we gather here",
    "start": 315.039,
    "duration": 4.481
  },
  {
    "text": "today for the first regular session of",
    "start": 317.36,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": "the common council, let us take a moment",
    "start": 319.52,
    "duration": 5.76
  },
  {
    "text": "to pause in gratitude and reflection. We",
    "start": 321.84,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "are grateful, oh God, for the",
    "start": 325.28,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "stewardship of our vibrant city.",
    "start": 327.12,
    "duration": 4.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Grateful for those who are committed to",
    "start": 329.44,
    "duration": 6.24
  },
  {
    "text": "service, to progress, and unity. I pray",
    "start": 331.36,
    "duration": 6.64
  },
  {
    "text": "for your divine presence to be with our",
    "start": 335.68,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "newly elected president Rita Piniagua",
    "start": 338.0,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "and all members of the common council.",
    "start": 340.32,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Their administrative staff as they lead",
    "start": 342.88,
    "duration": 5.84
  },
  {
    "text": "with excellence are courageous in the",
    "start": 345.6,
    "duration": 5.599
  },
  {
    "text": "face of challenges, discerning in their",
    "start": 348.72,
    "duration": 6.4
  },
  {
    "text": "priorities and faithful in their oaths.",
    "start": 351.199,
    "duration": 6.081
  },
  {
    "text": "Give them more resiliency, more resolve,",
    "start": 355.12,
    "duration": 4.639
  },
  {
    "text": "more patience, and more understanding.",
    "start": 357.28,
    "duration": 4.639
  },
  {
    "text": "God, let the distractions this year be",
    "start": 359.759,
    "duration": 6.081
  },
  {
    "text": "few and the advancement great. Let them",
    "start": 361.919,
    "duration": 5.681
  },
  {
    "text": "serve with willing hands and pure",
    "start": 365.84,
    "duration": 4.96
  },
  {
    "text": "hearts. Let their work leave a legacy",
    "start": 367.6,
    "duration": 6.08
  },
  {
    "text": "for others to follow and a blueprint",
    "start": 370.8,
    "duration": 6.08
  },
  {
    "text": "that's undeniably clear. We ask thy",
    "start": 373.68,
    "duration": 4.639
  },
  {
    "text": "blessings, oh God, upon the city of",
    "start": 376.88,
    "duration": 4.879
  },
  {
    "text": "Syracuse, its neighbors, its residents,",
    "start": 378.319,
    "duration": 6.241
  },
  {
    "text": "and all those who call her home. I",
    "start": 381.759,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "especially ask your blessings upon the",
    "start": 384.56,
    "duration": 4.639
  },
  {
    "text": "most vulnerable within our community,",
    "start": 386.479,
    "duration": 5.921
  },
  {
    "text": "our children, our elders, marginalized",
    "start": 389.199,
    "duration": 4.881
  },
  {
    "text": "populations, those who are hungry,",
    "start": 392.4,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "homeless, and home insecure, those in",
    "start": 394.08,
    "duration": 6.32
  },
  {
    "text": "need of help and hope. May our city be",
    "start": 396.56,
    "duration": 6.0
  },
  {
    "text": "blessed with safety and prosperity and",
    "start": 400.4,
    "duration": 4.32
  },
  {
    "text": "harmony. May our decisions serve the",
    "start": 402.56,
    "duration": 4.4
  },
  {
    "text": "greater good and foster an environment",
    "start": 404.72,
    "duration": 6.0
  },
  {
    "text": "of growth and opportunity.",
    "start": 406.96,
    "duration": 5.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, oh God, may the spirit of",
    "start": 410.72,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "collaboration and respect and purpose",
    "start": 412.4,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "fill our agendas as much as the business",
    "start": 415.44,
    "duration": 6.08
  },
  {
    "text": "of the day. And may each deliberation",
    "start": 418.56,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "results in making Syracuse whole and",
    "start": 421.52,
    "duration": 6.799
  },
  {
    "text": "healthy and hearted. God, may your",
    "start": 424.72,
    "duration": 6.08
  },
  {
    "text": "wisdom guide us. May your strength",
    "start": 428.319,
    "duration": 6.32
  },
  {
    "text": "search us. May your love compel us. May",
    "start": 430.8,
    "duration": 7.28
  },
  {
    "text": "your strength support us. We trust your",
    "start": 434.639,
    "duration": 6.96
  },
  {
    "text": "plans. In thy great name we pray. Amen.",
    "start": 438.08,
    "duration": 3.92
  },
  {
